'''Sublevel 12''' was a level of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] near the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]] and [[Roan Fel's private quarters]]. It contained [[LV8-series guard droid|guard droids]] protecting a ship. They were defeated by [[Roan Fel]] and his escort while [[Darth Krayt]] and his [[One Sith|Sith]] went after his decoy.

